---
import Navbar from "../components/navbar.astro";
import "../styles/main.css";
import "../styles/text.css"
---

<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>Clients | Consult Your Community</title>
        <link
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap"
            rel="stylesheet"
        />
    </head>

    <body style="margin: 0; font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
        <Navbar />

        <main style="padding: 120px 20px 60px; max-width: 70vw; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.8; text-align:center;">
            <h1 class="title-text-black">Partner with Us</h1>

            <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.1rem;">
                Interested in working with our student consultants? We'd love to
                help you grow your business.
            </p>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 2rem 0;">
                <a
                    href="https://forms.gle/sZn9oH6rDY8DyLpV8"
                    target="https://forms.gle/sZn9oH6rDY8DyLpV8"
                    class="cta-button"
                >
                    Sign Up via Google Form
                </a>
            </div>

            <hr style="margin: 3rem 0;" />

            <section>
                <div class="left-side-title-layout">
                    <div>
                        <h2 style="color: #232d62;">The Process</h2>
                        <p>
                            While the structure of an engagement will depend on your company's needs, this is the format most teams will follow.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="vertical-timeline">
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h3>Scoping Call</h3>
                                <p>
                                    A short virtual meeting to learn about your
                                    business, goals, and challenges. This helps us
                                    understand how our team can help.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
    
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h3>Engagement</h3>
                                <p>
                                    A team of analysts will work with you throughout the
                                    semester, meeting regularly and developing
                                    tailored recommendations.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
    
                        <div class="timeline-item">
                            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                            <div class="timeline-content">
                                <h3>Final Recommendation</h3>
                                <p>
                                    A comprehensive presentation and report
                                    summarize our findings, proposed solutions, and
                                    next steps.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
    </body>
</html>
